data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the desirable neighborhood of Maumee! With a full basement and abundant entertaining space, this spacious ranch is perfect for those who love to host gatherings. The open kitchen concept seamlessly flows into the dining and living areas, providing a seamless and inviting atmosphere. While the large lot provides ample outdoor space for relaxation and recreation. Don't miss the additional storage shed and the enticing inground pool, which has been thoughtfully winterized and eagerly awaits your enjoyment in the coming spring.
